############################ ASteCA's inner flags ##############################

# Update checker.
#
# * flag: y / n
#   Check if a new version of ASteCA is available for download, and notify the
#   user when one is found. Downloads less than 25 bytes of data and is thus
#   very quick.
#
#   flag
